title: Ep. 808 - The Misinformers
description:
The Biden White House calls to censor “misinformation,” a porn star shows up to a conservative student summit, and LA reinstates its mask mandate even for vaccinated Angelenos.
My new book ’Speechless: Controlling Words, Controlling Minds,’ is now available wherever books are sold. Grab your copy today here: https://utm.io/udtMJ
